OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain, the
OL,7,Frain clearing towards midnight to
OL,8,Fleave clear spells and a few showers
OL,9,Fthrough the early hours. A touch of
OL,10,Ffrost is possible in sheltered spots
OL,11,Fas the occasionally strong
OL,12,Fnorthwesterly winds ease.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FA few early showers, but for a
OL,15,Fmost a dry day with variable amounts
OL,16,Fof cloud and sunny intervals. Rather
OL,17,Fcold with the occasionally fresh
OL,18,Fnorthwesterly breeze continuing to
OL,19,Fease.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
